messages.author: Greg Spencer (Chromium)
messages.text:
On 2012/03/07 23:51:42, zel wrote:
> what is this used for

It keeps the value of whether this file is pinned or not until it can be read in DoOperation to set the actual pinned value on each file in the list.  Since DoOperation is still to be implemented, it's not yet actually used.
